 -- Jonas Smedegaard <dr@jones.dk>  Thu, 04 Apr 2024 21:17:09 +0200

nheko (0.11.3+~0.9.2+~1.0.0+~0.3.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * add myself as uploader
  * tighten buildflags
  * stop explicitly enable verbose build,
    to support DEB_BUILD_OPTIONS=terse
  * explicitly set buildsystem=cmake and use upstream install,
    concretely including SVG icon and zsh shell completion script
  * add patch 2003
    to avoid forcing ANSI colors in build logs
  * update copyright info:
    + use shortname Expat
    + use shortname Unlicense
    + update coverage
    + use License-Grant field
    + use Reference field
    + list License sections last, sorted alphabetically
    + list upstream right-truncated Files sections first
    + add Upstream-Contact field
    + add secondary source URIs
  * recommend (not depend on) gnome-keyring or kwalletmanager;
    add README.Debian notice
    about how to to disable use of secure secrets service;
    closes: bug#1016149,
    thanks to xiao sheng wen(肖盛文) and Hubert Chathi
  * update git-buildpackage config:
    + enable pristine-tar
    + enable signed tags
    + filter-out any .git* file
    + use DEP14 branches
    + add usage config
  * update watch file:
    + use substitution strings
    + set dversionmangle=auto
    + add usage config
    + track git commits (not release tags)
  * update watch file
    to track secondary tarballs a.k.a. embedded components;
    drop custom make target make-orig-source;
    closes: bug#926668, thanks to Linda Lapinlampi
  * add source helper script copyright-check
  * recommend gstreamer1.0-plugins-bad;
    closes: bug#1037156, thanks to Helmut Grohne

 -- Jonas Smedegaard <dr@jones.dk>  Thu, 29 Feb 2024 16:19:13 +0100

